    <abstract>
      <t>This document defines a YANG data model for the configuration and
   management of Routing in Fat Trees (RIFT) Protocol.  The model is
   based on YANG 1.1 as defined in RFC7950 and conforms to the Network
   Management Datastore Architecture (NMDA) as described in RFC8342.</t>
